SANGFOR VM Performance Optimization Tool Installation Instructions


-------------------------------------------------------

Installation Package
1.SangforVMSToolLinux.tar.gz   Installation Package

2.install.sh                   Installation Script

3.README                       Instruction File


--------------------------------------------------------
Steps:
1. Enter Web administrator console and log in to VM OS with Root privilege.

2. Switch to CD-ROM dir.
   Commands
   mkdir /mnt/cdrom                         Create CD-ROM drive
   mount /dev/sr1 /mnt/cdrom                Mount CD-ROM drive. If the drive is not mounted automatically, you need to execute the command manually.
   cd /mnt/cdrom                            Switch to CD-ROM dir

3. Run install.sh script to start installation.
   Command: ./install.sh

4. Follow the prompts to complete the installation.










